to art school.
Art school!

769
00:41:30,155 --> 00:41:32,021
He can't even
draw a breath
without fainting.

770
00:41:32,023 --> 00:41:33,256
(Laughing)

771
00:41:34,092 --> 00:41:35,258
Look, about your boy,

772
00:41:36,261 --> 00:41:37,861
