781
00:42:01,302 --> 00:42:01,951
Glenda: Mmm-hmm.
Mavis: What?

782
00:42:03,255 --> 00:42:05,889
Glenda:
She is giving him a ride.

783
00:42:05,891 --> 00:42:07,857
