a ride, so what?

784
00:42:08,760 --> 00:42:10,894
It's always
those quiet ones.

785
00:42:10,896 --> 00:42:12,662
(Car engine starting)

786
00:42:12,664 --> 00:42:14,931
You are
a wicked old broad
