00:48:07,452 --> 00:48:08,885
Lynne, demonstrate that.

907
00:48:08,887 --> 00:48:10,453
Okay.

908
00:48:10,455 --> 00:48:13,589
When you make the turn,
the left hand is on the cane,

909
00:48:13,591 --> 00:48:16,626
