00:48:21,332 --> 00:48:23,132
Don't move,
I want you down here
in the solo spot.

913
00:48:23,668 --> 00:48:25,234
Just stay there.

914
00:48:25,236 --> 00:48:27,036
Wait, we'll get it.
Let's try it again.

915
00:48:27,038 --> 00:48:28,437
Come on, here we go.
(Clears throat) And...

916
00:48:29,040 --> 00:48:30,439
(Vocalizing)

917
00:48:30,441 --> 00:48:32,575
