966
00:50:17,881 --> 00:50:18,546
You've only got
two t's, right,
Geoffrey?

967
00:50:20,218 --> 00:50:22,151
Don't worry, Geoffrey.
I've got plenty.

968
00:50:22,153 --> 00:50:23,386
