983
00:50:55,787 --> 00:50:57,119
Turn, go.

984
00:50:57,121 --> 00:50:58,754
(Vocalizing)

985
00:50:58,756 --> 00:51:02,291
And Geoffrey.
(Vocalizing)

986
00:51:02,293 --> 00:51:05,061
Turn.
